dct_title_s: Palaestina qvae et Terra Sancta vel terra promissionis
dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
4 bar scales on map given in "Leucae", "Mil. german.", "Stadia", and "Mil. italica".
Shows topography, vegetation, travel routes, places of historical interest.
Descriptive text following title and in left corner, e.g.: Hierusalem urbs clarissima...
